Package ch.unibe.iam.graph.io

Interface Summary
GraphReader Defines a common API for classes reading graph data from an input file.
GraphScheme This interface defines a common API for schemes of graph objects.
GraphSchemeWriter Defines a common API for classes writing graph scheme data to an output stream.
GraphWriter Defines a common API for classes writing graph data to an output stream.
GxlConstants Constants used when reading/writing in GXL.
Streamable Defines common API for GraphWriter classes which are streamable (i. e.
Writeable Defines common API for GraphWriter classes which are writeable (i. e.
 

Class Summary
AbstractGraphReader Provides some default functionality for all Reader classes.
AbstractGraphStream Provides some default functionality for all GraphWriter classes which use (binary) streams for output.
AbstractGraphWriter Provides some default functionality for all GraphWriter classes.
AbstractSchemeWriter Provides some default functionality for all SchemeWriter classes.
DimacsAsciiWriter Writes a graph in textual DIMACS format (Center for Discrete Mathematics and Theoretical Computer Science).
DimacsBinaryWriter Writes a graph in binary DIMACS format (Center for Discrete Mathematics and Theoretical Computer Science).
EdgeListReader Parses a text list of edges specified by its endpoints (vx1 <-> vx2) and builds the corresponding graph.
FsmReader Parses a text file in FSM and returns the corresponding graph object.
FsmWriter Writes a graph in Fsm (Finite State Machine) format.
GdlWriter Writes a graph in GDL (Graph Description Language) format.
GmlReader Parses a text file in GML and returns the corresponding graph object.
GmlWriter Writes a graph in GML (Graph Modelling Language) format.
GraphFormatsRegistry Central registry for registering all supported formats for reading or writing graphs.
GxlReader Parses a text file in GXL and returns the corresponding graph object.
GxlSaxHandler Writes a graph in GXL (XML) format.
GxlWriter Writes a graph in GXL format.
LGxlReader Parses a text file in GXL as used in Loeffels Shockgraph project (not fully following standards): - only one graph per gxl file - missing header/doctype information - invalid ids
MessmerReader Parses a text file in Messmer Format and returns the corresponding graph object.
MessmerScheme The messmer implementation of a graph scheme.
MessmerSchemeWriter Writes the scheme of a graph in the Messmer format.
MessmerWriter Writes a graph in Messmer format.
OtterReader Reads an undirected graph in Otter format.
OtterWriter Writes a graph in Otter format.
TrnReader Überschrift: Diplomarbeit Ähnlichkeit von Clusterings Beschreibung: Copyright: Copyright (c) 2003 Organisation: UniBE
TrnWriter Diplomarbeit Ähnlichkeit von Clusterings Writes graphs into files in the trn-format Copyright: Copyright (c) 2003 Organisation: UniBE
VflibReader Parses a text file in the VFLIB Format and returns the corresponding graph object.
VflibWriter Writes a graph in Vflib format.
